---
/** FAQ a ancho completo (landing). */
---

<section
  data-landing-reveal
  style="--lr-delay: 50ms"
  class="rounded-3xl border border-violet-200/50 dark:border-violet-900/40 bg-white/55 dark:bg-gray-950/45 shadow-sm overflow-hidden"
  aria-labelledby="landing-faq-heading"
>
  <div
    class="px-6 py-5 border-b border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800/70 bg-linear-to-r from-violet-50/60 via-white/55 to-transparent dark:from-violet-950/35 dark:via-gray-950/50 dark:to-transparent backdrop-blur"
  >
    <div class="space-y-1 max-w-3xl">
      <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-300 uppercase" data-i18n="landing.faqKicker">
        Ayuda
      </p>
      <h2 id="landing-faq-heading" class="m-0 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="landing.faqTitle">
        Preguntas frecuentes
      </h2>
      <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.faqIntro">
        Respuestas directas para quien llega sin sesión. Si necesitas algo más concreto, el contacto está abajo.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="p-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-3" style="overflow-anchor: none;">
      <details
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/55 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-violet-300/70 dark:hover:border-violet-800/60 open:border-violet-400/50 dark:open:border-violet-700/50"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 rounded-lg"
        >
          <span data-i18n="landing.faq1Q">¿Por qué solo por invitación?</span>
          <span class="text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 text-lg leading-none group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-900/60 pl-3" data-i18n="landing.faq1A">
          Para iterar sin fricción y cuidar la experiencia mientras el producto crece con cabeza.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/55 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-violet-300/70 dark:hover:border-violet-800/60 open:border-violet-400/50 dark:open:border-violet-700/50"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 rounded-lg"
        >
          <span data-i18n="landing.faq2Q">¿Qué es público hoy?</span>
          <span class="text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 text-lg leading-none group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-900/60 pl-3" data-i18n="landing.faq2A">
          Esta landing con demos visuales, precios orientativos y la página de contacto sin sesión. Si alguien comparte su portfolio, también verás esa URL pública. El resto de la app requiere invitación e inicio de sesión.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/55 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-violet-300/70 dark:hover:border-violet-800/60 open:border-violet-400/50 dark:open:border-violet-700/50"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 rounded-lg"
        >
          <span data-i18n="landing.faq3Q">¿Cómo pido acceso?</span>
          <span class="text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 text-lg leading-none group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-900/60 pl-3" data-i18n="landing.faq3A">
          Usa “Solicitar acceso” y cuenta tu caso. Respondemos cuando haya hueco.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/55 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-violet-300/70 dark:hover:border-violet-800/60 open:border-violet-400/50 dark:open:border-violet-700/50"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 rounded-lg"
        >
          <span data-i18n="landing.faq4Q">¿Qué sigue en desarrollo?</span>
          <span class="text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 text-lg leading-none group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-900/60 pl-3" data-i18n="landing.faq4A">
          Lo publicamos en el backlog por versiones. Entre otras líneas: más plantillas, PDF de portfolio, duplicar proyectos y monetización cuando toque.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/55 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-violet-300/70 dark:hover:border-violet-800/60 open:border-violet-400/50 dark:open:border-violet-700/50"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 rounded-lg"
        >
          <span data-i18n="landing.faq5Q">¿Dónde viven mis datos?</span>
          <span class="text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 text-lg leading-none group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-900/60 pl-3" data-i18n="landing.faq5A">
          Con sesión, el núcleo vive en Supabase (PostgreSQL) con RLS por cuenta. Herramientas del kit pueden guardar solo en tu navegador hasta que actives almacenamiento en la nube donde exista.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/55 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-violet-300/70 dark:hover:border-violet-800/60 open:border-violet-400/50 dark:open:border-violet-700/50"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 rounded-lg"
        >
          <span data-i18n="landing.faq6Q">¿Tengo que publicar portfolio o CV?</span>
          <span class="text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 text-lg leading-none group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-900/60 pl-3" data-i18n="landing.faq6A">
          No. Puedes trabajar todo en privado y encender enlaces públicos solo cuando quieras, desde Ajustes.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/55 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-violet-300/70 dark:hover:border-violet-800/60 open:border-violet-400/50 dark:open:border-violet-700/50"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 rounded-lg"
        >
          <span data-i18n="landing.faq7Q">¿Qué son los precios de la web?</span>
          <span class="text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 text-lg leading-none group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-900/60 pl-3" data-i18n="landing.faq7A">
          Una guía orientativa para equipos y uso personal. Los cargos reales llegarán con términos claros cuando activemos facturación.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details
        class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/85 dark:bg-gray-950/55 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-violet-300/70 dark:hover:border-violet-800/60 open:border-violet-400/50 dark:open:border-violet-700/50"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500 rounded-lg"
        >
          <span data-i18n="landing.faq8Q">¿Hay app nativa?</span>
          <span class="text-violet-500 dark:text-violet-400 text-lg leading-none group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-900/60 pl-3" data-i18n="landing.faq8A">
          Hoy SkillAtlas es una web app moderna (navegador). Priorizamos flujo de escritorio; el móvil va mejorando de forma incremental.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
